<p>Like all Chateau Collection beverage and wine refrigerators, the (<strong>6SBARE</strong>) comes equipped with the exclusive Sentry System? refrigeration monitor with visual and audible alarms for over/under temperature, power failure and door ajar conditions. Intuitive digital touch controls with a <a class="zem_slink" title="Light-emitting diode" rel="wikipedia" href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Light-emitting_diode">blue LED</a> display allows the temperature to be easily set and monitored. Other features include full auto defrost, soft interior lighting that can be set to continuous illumination, a right hinged door and a built-in user-activated Sabbath mode.</p>
